This indicator can integrate som of the following elements:
Training sessions/workshops held	Number per year or adaptation cycle
Participants trained	Total number, disaggregated by group
Educational programs/courses developed (Number of new or revised curricula);
Capacity building materials produced (Number of manuals, toolkits, online resources);
Technical assistance missions	(Number of expert visits/coaching sessions);
Awareness campaigns conducted	(Number per year, by audience);
Campaign reach/engagement	(People reached, participation rates, behavioral change);
Change in awareness/knowledge (Pre/post survey scores, % increase in awareness
Stakeholder participation	Number/type of organizations involved).
Institutional capacity assessment	Scores or qualitative ratings of institutional readiness
